00:16:58,560 --> 00:16:59,320
I'm in.

295
00:17:02,560 --> 00:17:03,440
He's in too.

296
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,119
Dou Congming.

297
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,240
Inspector Zhang,

298
00:17:12,599 --> 00:17:13,930
my name is Dou Mingcong.

299
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:17,359
They want to solve cases.

300
00:17:17,359 --> 00:17:18,599
Shanghai is so big,

301
