302
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:20,720
Zhao Erbao.

303
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,359
Transfer to Criminal Investigation Section 4 first.

304
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:26,089
Come back when it's disbanded.

305
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:26,880
No.

306
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,720
I...

307
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:31,200
Understood.

308
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:31,920
I'll join.

309
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:35,620
Within three days.

310
